Global Building Energy Management Software Market Insights
Building Energy Management Software Market size was valued at USD 4.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.93 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Building Energy Management Software Market Overview
The global Building Energy Management Software (BEMS) market has been witnessing significant growth, with a market value expected to reach USD 15.89 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 13.5% from 2025 to 2030. The increasing demand for energy-efficient buildings, government regulations for energy conservation, and rising concerns about environmental sustainability are driving the adoption of BEMS solutions. This market is benefiting from the growing focus on smart buildings, the integration of IoT in energy management, and advancements in cloud-based technologies. Additionally, the market is being propelled by the increasing need for real-time energy monitoring and optimization in commercial and residential infrastructures.

